Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.32,1:21:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.93,1:22:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,β-三尖戟——
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.19,1:22:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发动
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.45,1:23:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是——
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.58,1:23:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.70,1:24:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.30,1:24:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务…虽然不是 完成了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.17,1:25:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见哦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.90,1:25:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.58,1:25:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重
