Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.50,1:29:08.48,OPJ@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}higher
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.48,1:29:12.48,OPJ@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか辿りつけるまで
