Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.95,1:25:32.82,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}直至抵达那里的那一天
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.62,1:25:45.28,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}宇宙中的光
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.28,1:25:47.55,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}多得让人生恨
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.55,1:25:50.21,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天也为射入的光线
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.24,1:25:52.79,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而烦恼头晕吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.79,1:25:55.21,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被迷惑的可不是你
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.21,1:25:57.64,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「你想要做什么？」
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.64,1:26:00.34,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看上去只当个乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.34,1:26:02.97,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是无法得到想要的东西的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.97,1:26:05.39,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}下好决心
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.39,1:26:07.51,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}目的地只有一个
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.52,1:26:11.28,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}瞄准之后 立刻开始
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.24,1:26:14.63,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I’m a speed of light star
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.63,1:26:17.41,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就如那彗星一般
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.43,1:26:22.45,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将悲伤和寂寞通通踢飞
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.45,1:26:27.46,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}甚至连畏惧的过去都黯然褪色
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.51,1:26:32.68,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就连光速都能超越 奔驰下去
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.68,1:26:35.23,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Fly higher
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.23,1:26:39.10,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}直至抵达那里的那一天
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.95,1:26:51.66,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}宇宙无限地延展得
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.66,1:26:54.02,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人舒爽
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.02,1:26:56.57,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}把那飘渺的「拜托」
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.57,1:26:59.10,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}通通擦掉说再见啦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.10,1:27:01.75,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果强烈地渴望
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.75,1:27:04.18,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就让它响到传达到为止
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.18,1:27:06.79,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.79,1:27:08.91,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}至少我会用我的双眼找到
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.91,1:27:11.27,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若你升起
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.27,1:27:13.98,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}火花四射 如烧如灼的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.98,1:27:17.61,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}火热心愿 就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.70,1:27:20.94,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I’m a speed of light star
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.94,1:27:23.81,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就如那彗星一般
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.81,1:27:28.87,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将痛苦与难过全都甩在身后
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.87,1:27:33.97,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不再需要看烦了的地图
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.97,1:27:39.06,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再痛也不怕 奔跑下去
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.06,1:27:41.70,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Fly higher
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.70,1:27:45.86,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}直至抵达那里的那一天
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.06,1:27:58.21,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果选择默默听从的话
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.21,1:28:00.88,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}该会有多轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.88,1:28:02.58,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}『我想要坦率地活下去』
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.58,1:28:05.32,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这也算是强词夺理吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.32,1:28:10.41,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}完美的活法不可能存在
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.41,1:28:15.07,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}抱歉我不能像课本一样去活
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.07,1:28:18.79,OPC@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无论谁说我什么都无所谓
